 {'is_revised': True, 'text': 'So there are 2 steps we need to do to convert the mixed number into an improper fraction', 'user': 'tutor'}
 {'is_revised': True, 'text': 'Step 1: Multiply the whole number part by the denominator', 'user': 'tutor'}
 {'is_revised': True, 'text': 'Step 2: Take the numerator and add it to the result of step 1', 'user': 'tutor'}
