 {'is_revised': True, 'text': 'Obviously we can\'t actually draw a line or a ray going on forever, so the "going on forever" part is represented by an arrow', 'user': 'tutor'}
 {'is_revised': True, 'text': 'Here is a picture comparing what a segment, ray, and line look like: https://tinyurl.com/38ydfk2t', 'user': 'tutor'}
 {'is_revised': True, 'text': 'Can you see something that looks like a ray in the diagram?', 'user': 'tutor'}
